userInput: The Last Stand: Amid a storm of fire and ash, a group of ragged warriors makes their final stand against a horde of shadowy creatures. A glowing magical barrier protects them, but cracks are beginning to form.

The Forgotten Temple: A team of explorers steps into an ancient jungle temple covered in vines and moss. Sunlight streams through cracks in the stone, illuminating a golden idol resting on a pedestal.
Escape Through the City: Under the pale glow of neon signs, a rogue hacker dashes through the rain-soaked streets of a cyberpunk city, pursued by drone enforcers.
